01:07:00.853 --> 01:07:03.853
But you don't say laughing out loud,

01:07:05.172 --> 01:07:07.911
for the kids lol was laughing out loud.

01:07:07.911 --> 01:07:09.072
But I think it has morphed,

01:07:09.072 --> 01:07:11.232
and it isn't really
about laughter anymore.

01:07:11.232 --> 01:07:14.158
It's just one more way to signal,

01:07:14.158 --> 01:07:16.325
don't take this literally.

01:07:22.308 --> 01:07:25.234
- Thanks so much for
